    <CMUI_Label name="lblHeading" id="0f910ed0-673d-4ecf-a40e-d213a9771787">
        <stretchHeight/>
        <caption>Use this window to copy the Ports of Call and the Operators (associated with the Debtors) from this Shipping Line Port Group to a Trade.
From JMT 7.7.2 the system uses the Trade to determine the default Ports of Call and Operators for a voyage, rather than the Shipping Line Port Group.
This window enables existing users to easily copy the valid Ports of Call and Operators from a Shipping Line Port Group to a Trade.</caption>
        <transparent/>
        <wordWrap/>
        <fontSize>8.25</fontSize>
        <foreColor>-2147483640</foreColor>
